{"content": "I need to multiply 311 \u00d7 155 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 311\u2089 = 3\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 243 + 9 + 1 = 253\u2081\u2080\n- 155\u2089 = 1\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 81 + 45 + 5 = 131\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 253 \u00d7 131 = 33,143\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 33143 \u00f7 9 = 3682 r 5\n- 3682 \u00f7 9 = 409 r 1\n- 409 \u00f7 9 = 45 r 4\n- 45 \u00f7 9 = 5 r 0\n- 5 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 5\n\nReading from bottom to top: 50415\u2089\n\n**Verification:**\n- 50415\u2089 = 5\u00d76561 + 0\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 32805 + 0 + 324 + 9 + 5 = 33143\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n50415", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 353}